#

Carrot Smoothie

5 min
$3.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy (if yogurt is used)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

SmoothieHealthyQuick

Description

A refreshing and nutritious smoothie packed with the goodness of carrots, perfect for a quick breakfast or snack!

Ingredients

  • carrots: 2 medium, peeled and chopped
  • banana: 1 ripe
  • orange juice: 1 cup
  • greek yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • honey: 1 tablespoon (optional)
  • ice cubes: 1/2 cup (optional)
